message.content: cs.LO, cs.LO is the most likely category as the paper deals with logic and its extensions. Other likely categories could be cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as the paper discusses the model-checking problem, cs.PL (Programming Languages) as the paper deals with operators and their syntax, cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) as the paper discusses path quantifiers and temporal operators, and cs.CC (Computational Complexity) as the paper analyzes the complexity of the model-checking problem.
